{
  "texts": [
    "The final set of 115 papers comprises 106 research papers, 6 platform or tool papers, and 3 surveys or introductory articles.",
    "The distribution of their publication venues is illustrated in Fig. 2.",
    "35% appeared in established software engineering conferences and journals, including 13 at ICSE, 8 at ASE, 6 at FSE, and 5 at ISSTA.",
    "An additional 9% were published in specialized venues focused on software quality or testing.",
    "Notably, 33% of the collected papers are non-peer-reviewed preprints available exclusively on arXiv."
  ]
}